lead_paragraph: Belgian Greg van Avermaet claimed the overall leader's yellow jersey when he won the fifth stage of the Tour de France at the end of a long breakaway as Alberto Contador appeared to suffer from crash-related injuries on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Van Avermaet Wins Tour De France Stage Five, Takes Yellow
